"Lynce": "Thank you. I'm so glad to hear you say that."
"As you can see, we have many injured ARKS here."
"I want to keep our patients well-nourished, but our food stockpiles are dangerously low right now..."
"So, I need you to go and get some Tames meat. The people here should recover in no time if they can get some meat to eat."
"I know I'm asking you to go out of your way for me, but we really need this. Take care of yourself out there."
